Subject: offline temporary passwords not working after EPP server power outage
Description:
Hi. We had a UPS failure and the EPP server VM lost power. When power came back, the server needed a file system repair so I hit 'f' and it booted. WebUI was working and i didn't see any other errors. Later that day a user tried to issue a temp password to another user to mount an external drive and the drive wouldn't mount. I tested on a different client and it didn't work there either. 
thanks, Andy
Solution_Comment__c: Re-synced server time -> OTP codes worked after that.
